             <div class="text-block">
              <h2 class="h1">Step 1.</h2>
              <p><span>First, get a pen and paper, look through our</span> <span>collections and make a note of 3 items you like</span> that would suit what you are looking for.</p>
             </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-5">
