               <p><span>Then, upload a photo of yourself,</span> <span>standing up full shot.</span>
               Please follow this example.</p>
             </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-7">
             <div class="img-block padding-left">
               <img src="{{"request-step2-img.jpg" | asset_url }}" alt="img">
             </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-12 order-3 col-sm-12 order-sm-3 col-md-5 order-md-1">
             <div class="img-block">
               <img src="{{"request-step3-img.jpg" | asset_url }}" alt="img">
             </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 order-1 col-sm-12 order-sm-1 col-md-7 order-md-2">
             <div class="text-block padding-left">
               <h1>Step 3.</h1>
               <p><span>Finally, provide your basic measurements:</span> Bust, waist, hips, height.</p>
             </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 order-2 col-sm-12 order-sm-2 col-md-8 order-md-3 col-lg-6 order-lg-3 m-auto">
